Title: An Act Changing the Name of Bulusan Elementary School in the City of Dagupan, to Don Jose De Venecia, Sr., Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 218
An Act Changing the Name of Bulusan Elementary School in the City of Dagupan, to Don Jose De Venecia, Sr., Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Bulusan Elementary School in the City of Dagupan is changed to Don Jose de Venecia, Sr., Memorial School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
